threads.title: 820-00164  no power
threads.message:
Arrived with no liquid damage. Q7630 was severely burned. Replaced then found U7600 was getting very hot and replaced that as well.

When turned on power board is power cycling. PPBUS_G3H and PPBUS_S5_HS_COMPUTING_INSIS steady 8.60V

Vcore pulses to 1.6V every few seconds.

What should be checked next?
